    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. Mechanically, this example is robust; the VANOS system has been overhauled, rod bearings replaced, and the rear subframe reinforced\u2014addressing all critical platform weak points. The suspension retains its composure with updated bushings and dampers, providing the tactile steering feedback these chassis are known for. While the exterior shows minor stone chipping and light patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the drivetrain remains in peak operational condition for the purist seeking performance over concours perfection.",
