      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2013 Porsche Boxster that perfectly captures the essence of open-top driving. Finished in a sophisticated Agate Grey Metallic, the exterior retains a brilliant shine, though it shows a few honest stone chips on the front fascia from spirited weekend drives. Inside, the black leather interior is clean and smoke-free, with only light softening on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health; the 2.7L engine is responsive, and the PDK transmission provides seamless shifts. I have curated a full service history, including a recent major interval service, new brake pads, and a fresh set of premium tires. The power convertible top is taut and operates perfectly without any leaks. This is a turn-key example for someone who values mechanical integrity and a well-documented past. It drives straight, sounds fantastic, and is ready for the open road.",
